OL,3,C'It's a war crime': ITV News' Gaza
OL,4,Cclip sparks outrage
OL,6,FRishi Sunak and the US were quizzed
OL,7,Fover an ITV News video which shows a
OL,8,Fcivilian being shot dead while in a
OL,9,Fgroup carrying a white flag in Gaza,
OL,10,Fmany say this shows a 'war crime,'
OL,11,FJohn Irvine and Robert Moore report
OL,13,FThe "shocking video" of a man part of
OL,14,Fa group waving a white flag being shot
OL,15,Fdead in Gaza, released by ITV News,
OL,16,Fhas sparked accusations of a "war
OL,17,Fcrime".
