OL,3,C'It's a war crime': ITV News' Gaza
OL,4,Cclip sparks outrage
OL,6,FLeading charities including Amnesty
OL,7,FInternational and the Norwegian
OL,8,FRefugee Council condemned the
OL,9,Fincident, while Rishi Sunak plus top
OL,10,FUS officials were quizzed on their
OL,11,Freaction today.
OL,13,FOn Tuesday, footage filmed by Mohammed
OL,14,FAbu Safia, a cameraman working for ITV
OL,15,FNews, , who wanted to rescue their
OL,16,Ffamily after being forced to evacuate
OL,17,Ftheir homes.
OL,19,FMinutes later, one of the men - Ramzi
OL,20,FAbu Sahloul - was fatally shot in the
OL,21,Fchest.
