OL,3,C'It's a war crime': ITV News' Gaza
OL,4,Cclip sparks outrage
OL,6,FSpeaking to ITV News, Jan Egeland
OL,7,Fsaid: "It's an absolutely shocking
OL,8,Fvideo... civilians are protected,
OL,9,Fprecautions should be taken to shield
OL,10,Fthem - it's not debatable the law is
OL,11,Fvery clear.
OL,13,F"If it was the Israel Defence Force
OL,14,F(IDF) you could charge commanders
OL,15,Fhere, it's utterly important there
OL,16,Fwill be accountability."
OL,18,FFrancesca Albanese, UN Special
OL,19,FRapporteur on the occupied Palestinian
OL,20,Fterritories, described the incident as
OL,21,F"a televised war crime".
