OL,3,C'It's a war crime': ITV News' Gaza
OL,4,Cclip sparks outrage
OL,6,FDuring Wednesday's Prime Minister's
OL,7,FQuestions, Stephen Flynn said: "Last
OL,8,Fnight, as Tory MPs were once again
OL,9,Ffighting amongst themselves, the
OL,10,Fpublic were sat at home watching John
OL,11,FIrvine of ITV News report on footage
OL,12,Ffrom Gaza of an unarmed Palestinian
OL,13,Fman, walking under a white flag, being
OL,14,Fshot and killed by the IDF.
OL,16,F"Prime Minister, such an act
OL,17,Fconstitutes a war crime, does it not?"
OL,1,Wz5~k4~k7}hw1 ~k4~sj5j5~s1 G     G6/14
