OL,6,FRishi Sunak does not condemn the
OL,7,Fshooting of an unarmed man in Gaza as
OL,8,Fa 'war crime' but he does say he is
OL,9,F'concerned' about the loss of civilian
OL,10,Flife in the enclave
OL,12,FLabour leader Sir Keir Starmer said he
OL,13,Fhadn't seen the footage when asked
OL,14,Fabout it on ITV's Peston on Wednesday
OL,15,Fnight.
OL,17,FAfter being asked about it again in an
OL,18,Fexclusive interview with ITV News, Sir
OL,19,FKeir said he still hadn't seen the
OL,20,Ffootage.
